import React from 'react'; import { Link } from 'react-router-dom'; import { motion } from 'framer-motion'; import { useCart } from '../contexts/CartContext'; import { TrashIcon, MinusIcon, PlusIcon, ShoppingBagIcon } from '@heroicons/react/24/outline'; const CartPage: React.FC = () => { const { items, updateQuantity, removeFromCart, getTotalPrice, getTotalItems } = useCart(); if (items.length === 0) { return (

Your cart is empty

Looks like you haven't added any items to your cart yet.

Start Shopping
); } return (

Shopping Cart

{/* Cart Items */}

Cart Items ({getTotalItems()})

{items.map((item, index) => (
{/* Product Image */}
{/* Product Details */}

{item.name}

${item.price} each

Stock: {item.stock}

{/* Quantity Controls */}
{item.quantity}
{/* Price */}

${(item.price * item.quantity).toFixed(2)}

{/* Remove Button */}
))}
{/* Order Summary */}

Order Summary

Subtotal ${getTotalPrice().toFixed(2)}
Shipping $0.00
Tax $0.00
Total ${getTotalPrice().toFixed(2)}
Proceed to Checkout Continue Shopping
); }; export default CartPage;
